        <p><sourcexml>bodytext</sourcexml> becomes <targetxml>seclaw:bodytext</targetxml>. If a
                <sourcexml>level</sourcexml> contains multiple sibling
                <sourcexml>bodytext</sourcexml> elements, then they should be merged into a single
                <targetxml>seclaw:bodytext</targetxml> element in the target.</p>
