        &lt;title&gt;Stages of an investigation&lt;/title&gt;
    &lt;/heading&gt;
    &lt;seclaw:bodytext&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;
            &lt;text&gt;The different stages of a European Commission investigation are set out in the
